These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, designer, manager
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, fonseca, game
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skateboarding, snowboarding
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, card-games, filmmaking
1. the game-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
5. the designer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
6. the game-smoker is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2       |     3      |
| Job           | dancer        | designer     | manager    |
| Cigar   | game      | bongani     | fonseca |
| Sport         | skateboarding | snowboarding | handball   |
| Hobby     | filmmaking        | card-games      | photography        |

