.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-2::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, ebony, red
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, skiing, weightlifting
3 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, train
1. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the owner of the frog and the person who likes emerald##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is the person who likes emerald##1
4. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person driving the train##1
5. the person who likes emerald is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |      3      |
| Color    | ebony    | red | emerald |
| Sport       | skiing   | weightlifting  | water-polo  |
| Pet         | frog      | fish     | goldfish    |
| Transport   | motorbike | train    | ship        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, skiing
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, lemonade, almond-milk
There are 3 different nationalities: french, italian, spanish
3 different pets are kept: bird, lizard, rat
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person drinking coffee is on the far left or far right##3
3. the owner of the lizard is between the owner of the bird and the person drinking almond-milk##2
4. the spanish is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
5. the italian is the italian##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |
| Sport         | skiing | cycling | snowboarding |
| Beverage           | almond-milk     | lemonade    | coffee |
| Nationality   | french      | spanish     | italian |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard      | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, pop, funk
3 different pets are kept: turtle, lizard, hedgehog
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, singing, writing
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, canadian, nigerian
1. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the australian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the person who's hobby is singing is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the hedgehog is between the nigerian and the owner of the turtle##2
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the canadian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | pop | r&b       | funk   |
| Pet          | turtle   | hedgehog   | lizard     |
| Hobby         | singing  | puzzles    | writing  |
| Nationality   | canadian | australian | nigerian |

