.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, sprite
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, alhambra, ritmeester
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, indie
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, december, january
1. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person drinking cola and the person drinking milk##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
3. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the fan of classical##1
5. the person drinking sprite is between the alhambra-smoker and the ritmeester-smoker##2
6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of indie##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage      | milk   | sprite    | cola   |
| Cigar          | ritmeester | havana  | alhambra |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | classical | indie  |
| Birthday     | november | december   | january  |

