.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-6::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, lemon, pomegranate
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, quad-bike, trike
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, thriller, time-travel
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, water
1. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
3. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
4. the person eating asparagus is the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
6. the person eating asparagus is the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching action movies is between the person drinking water and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |      3       |
| Food          | asparagus | lemon    | pomegranate  |
| Transport           | quad-bike      | jet-ski  | trike |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller  | action   | time-travel  |
| Beverage           | almond-milk      | mirinda | water        |

