.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-7::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, soy-milk
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, chef, electrician
City: san-francisco, hannover, london
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, daffodil, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the chef##1
2. the accountant is the person traveling to london##1
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
4. the person traveling to hannover is in the middle##1
5. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
6. the accountant is the person drinking lemonade##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
8. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2       |     3      |
| Beverage   | 7up         | soy-milk      | lemonade   |
| Job        | electrician | chef          | accountant |
| City        | san-francisco         | hannover        | london       |
| Flower      | daffodil       | balloon-flower | begonia       |

