.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-8::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, malaysian, italian
House: art-deco, colonial, gothic-revival
3 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig, mouse
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, trike
1. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the bus##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the malaysian##1
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person driving the jet-ski##3
4. the italian is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
5. the italian is the person driving the trike##1
6. the gothic-revival house is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Nationality       | italian | turkish    | malaysian |
| House         | art-deco   | colonial | gothic-revival     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig  | mouse     | frog        |
| Transport   | trike       | jet-ski   | bus         |

