There 3 different types of food: banana, blueberry, pineapple
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, red, lavender
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, bus, helicopter
1. the person eating banana is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
2. the teacher is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
3. the person who likes azure is on the far right##1
4. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the pilot##1
5. the teacher is the person eating blueberry##1
6. the person driving the bike is the person who likes azure##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |      3      |
| Job      | teacher       | pilot | writer |
| Food          | blueberry  | banana | pineapple   |
| Color   | red    | lavender   | azure        |
| Transport     | helicopter | bus    | bike        |

