The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, zinnia
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, classical, d&b
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, yellow, emerald
1. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
2. the person who likes yellow is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3
3. the person who likes yellow is the person who likes yellow##1
4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
5. the fan of classical is the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes yellow##2
7. the fan of d&b is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
