.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-11::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, balloon-flower, azalea
3 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, golf, rugby
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bongani, pall-mall
1. the owner of the lizard is between the person who growsazalea and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is baseball##3
4. the game-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
6. the bongani-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |    3     |
| Flower       | azalea   | balloon-flower | daffodil  |
| Pet         | pony      | lizard      | ferret   |
| Sport       | golf      | rugby       | baseball |
| Cigar   | game | pall-mall       | bongani     |

