.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-12::.
There 3 different types of food: nectarine, pineapple, watermelon
The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, librarian, manager
City: hamburg, boston, miami
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard, scooter
1. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the engineer##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the manager##3
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the far right##1
7. the person traveling to boston is between the engineer and the librarian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon | nectarine | pineapple |
| Job           | engineer   | manager   | librarian |
| City   | miami     | boston     | hamburg  |
| Transport   | skateboard     | scooter  | jet-ski   |

