.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, hot-chocolate, mirinda
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, old-henry, pall-mall
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, puzzles
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: time-travel, family, epic
1. the pall-mall-smoker is between the davidoff-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the pall-mall-smoker is between the person watching family movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the old-henry-smoker##3
7. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |      3      |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | mirinda    | almond-milk |
| Cigar       | old-henry          | pall-mall     | davidoff       |
| Hobby      | puzzles       | card-games | board-games |
| Movie-Genre        | family          | epic       | time-travel        |

