.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-14::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, september, may
3 different games are played: monopoly, scrabble, poker
3 different pets are kept: cat, rat, turtle
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, cycling, handball
1. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1
3. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
6. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |
| Birthday   | may     | august   | september   |
| Game   | scrabble   | poker | monopoly |
| Pet           | cat        | turtle    | rat       |
| Sport         | basketball | cycling   | handball  |

