3 different games are played: domino, backgammon, bridge
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, baking, magic-tricks
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, rugby, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the person playing backgammon is the person who's hobby is baking##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is drawing##3
5. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person playing bridge and the person playing backgammon##2
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | water    | lemonade   | fanta      |
| Game   | bridge | domino   | backgammon |
| Hobby           | drawing      | magic-tricks      | baking      |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | rugby      |

