The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, freelancer, lawyer
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, bike, jet-ski
3 different pets are kept: cat, frog, rabbit
1. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is the person playing canasta##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the subway is on the far left##1
5. the freelancer is between the person playing chess and the lawyer##2
6. the person driving the jet-ski is the lawyer##1
7. the freelancer is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |
| Game         | chess      | bridge     | canasta |
| Job           | entrepreneur | freelancer | lawyer     |
| Transport   | subway    | bike       | jet-ski      |
| Pet           | cat          | frog       | rabbit     |

