3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the craftsman house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the palace house##3
6. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the tower house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | fanta        | mirinda |
| House   | craftsman | palace | tower  |
| Sport         | handball  | biathlon     | surfing |
| Birthday     | march      | january   | september    |

