3. the person who's birthday is in october is between the egyptian and the person eating garlic##2
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
5. the person eating garlic is on the left of the italian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
7. the person eating garlic is the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Food        | garlic       | peach     | cucumber   |
| Nationality         | colombian          | italian    | egyptian       |
| Birthday       | may | october | september |
| Transport   | bus          | van       | skateboard |

