.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-3-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, juice, mirinda
There 3 different types of food: orange, carrot, spinach
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, fantasy
House: farmhouse, colonial, townhouse
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the colonial house is on the far right##1
4. the person eating orange is on the far left##1
5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the farmhouse house##1
8. the person watching comedy movies is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda | juice  | hot-chocolate |
| Food           | orange  | spinach  | carrot      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | comedy | animation     |
| House           | townhouse  | farmhouse | colonial         |

 